entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="chin" o="等我喺度出人頭地，我就會翻返去。" t="I'll go back to China once I make something of myself here." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="chin" o="我唔想返去。" t="I'm never going back." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="chin" o="你想將時間都浪費喺度呀？人哋一世咋。" t="You wanna waste what time you got? Here? You only get one life." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="chin" o="係吖，咁你做咗啲咩？除咗搵雞叫，增加閱歷…" t="Well yeah… and what're you doing with yours? Besides having fun, collecting \"experiences\"…" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="chin" o="你一定要做啲咩？留低啲乜嘢？" t="You gotta do something. Leave something behind." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="chin" o="圍邊個？" t="For what?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="chin" o="為咗屋企人囉。" t="For your family." b="" a=""/>
